    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Heavy, usually steel or iron blocks, on which metal is shaped by hand hammering or forging. Anvils are also used for working materials other than metal.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
